        "y": 300
      },
      "width": 400,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "body": "Trim the radial menu so it accelerates common actions without carrying management or discovery burden. The first pass is in: management and reference surfaces like Legend, Document, Inspect, Minimap, and Elements inventory have been removed from the radial menu so it reads more like a shortcut surface.",
