        "body": "Per-edge styling already belongs in edge properties, but the product still needs a home for graph-wide default edge appearance. Do not keep that authority in the layout panel. Evaluate whether graph-wide edge defaults should live in the theme node, future edge classes, or another authored visual surface.",
