        "summary": "The browser now has a real home for account state, but the identity model is still mid-flight. Twilite account creation now exists and is the correct primary authority, GitHub can restore a linked Twilite account for returning users, and provider linking has started to take shape. The remaining gap is Twilite-native re-entry for users who already have a Twilite account but no linked provider, plus explicit secondary-provider support such as Google.",
